  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Same spatial extent. Symmetric and transitive. Reflexivity is part of the intended RCC8 semantics but is not declared in OWL because ReflexiveProperty without domain/range would apply to all individuals, and with domain/range would force everything to be a Region."
